{"lastModified":1761073135066,"uri":"c::7584683786::vessel::d5cc790b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Though TEMPEST WS was built in 1962, this super yacht only gets better with age. She was refitted in 2011 and now boasts the history of a yachting world stalwart as well as a modern interior and exterior thanks to Esterel and Andre Mauric. \nTEMPEST WS is never short of space, with three tiers worth of decking to choose from when laying out the sunbeds for the day. Below decks, there are four cabins that sleep eight guests, as well as added capacity for five crew to ensure that your journey is every Boolean as blissful as it possibly could be. Each cabin is decked out with decadent furnishings that tie in with a chrome and dark caramel colour scheme. TEMPEST WS cruises at 18 knots and is powered by a modern motor. On board, there is also a RIB Tender to take you from A to B, as well as jet skis, waterskis, wakeboards, snorkeling gear and inflatable toys to provide endless hours of fun.  A top pick for those wishing to cruise the Mediterranean, TEMPEST WS truly does have it all. \n","blueprint":{"name":"TEMPEST WS","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc790b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yacht-image-2820-full-1_HERO.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc790b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yacht-image-3339-full-1.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc790b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yacht-image-2821-full-4.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc790b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yacht-image-2822-full-6.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc790b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yacht-image-2823-full-2.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc790b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yacht-image-3340-full-3.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc790b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yac